Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你太過分了 Panty
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好呀 Geek boy 金幣集齊沒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
