Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.76,0:22:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Corset你這傢夥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好久不見啊 Garterbelt
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.21,0:22:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,自那次以後就一直沒有像這樣面對面了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.47,0:22:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 市長先生為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.06,0:22:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,因為天使的吻 Hellsmonkey的血族得以覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.47,0:22:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是我們一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,苦苦等待的東西啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.50,0:23:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 我終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.06,0:23:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我的小○雞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Panty 快帶上Brief趕緊逃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.13,0:23:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.33,0:23:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我說是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是連拿手的啪啪啪都沒辦法幹的處○天使嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.12,0:23:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 小心她傳染給你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.69,0:23:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Demon姐妹 把Hellsmonkey給我帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是 那麼我們就失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.27,0:23:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Panty!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.46,0:23:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Geek boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.32,0:23:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.94,0:23:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你們完蛋了 接下來我們毫不留情的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.10,0:23:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就開始了!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.02,0:23:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,無能的天使們 你們就為自己犯下的過錯痛苦一輩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.99,0:24:22.80,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Heaven, please sing for me a song of life
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.05,0:24:27.80,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Heaven, take me into your skies
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.05,0:24:32.51,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}There's no place here for me to hide my cries
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.51,0:24:35.42,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Night and day I'm missing you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.60,0:24:39.60,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}You're so close (so close)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.78,0:24:43.15,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}And it's you that I believe in (I believe in)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.15,0:24:48.03,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}So close, but far away so far I can't touch
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.03,0:24:52.11,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}I'll hold on, 'cause it's you I love so dearly
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.11,0:24:54.97,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}When the rain, the storm and all is up
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.16,0:24:58.14,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Caress me with your sweet lullaby
